#{{biochemistry}} any of several [[isomeric]] [[cyclic]] [[polyhydric]] [[alcohol]]s, C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>12</sub>O<sub>6</sub>, found in both plant and animal tissue.

===Usage notes===
* Once treated as a [[component]] of the [[vitamin B complex]], but is not a [[vitamin]] as it can be synthesized by the body.

